fulltitle: Jazz Inspired-Tony Bennett on Bill Evans.mov
description:
Judy Carmichael recorded a special two-part conversation with Tony Bennett on her Public Radio show "Jazz Inspired".  Judy and Tony talk about  his long career, his classic recordings with pianist Bill Evans and his recent collaboration with an all-star cast (Lady Gaga, Amy Winehouse, Michael Bublé) on his new CD, "Duets II". 

In this clip, Tony talks about the process he and Bill Evans used in conceptualizing the songs for "The Tony Bennett and Bill Evans Album".

http://jazzinspired.com/
http://judycarmichael.com/

Video by Rich Ficara
